  - [ ] Use the latest ViroReact release: https://docs.viromedia.com/docs/releases

## Environment
Please provide the following information about your environment:
1. OS: Mac, Windows, Linux
2. Platform: iOS or Android or both
3. Version: ViroReact version and React Native version 
4. Device: What device are you are seeing the issue on (i.e. iPhone X, Samsung Note 8, etc)

## Description
Describe your issue in detail. Include screenshots if needed. If this is a regression, let us know.

## Reproducible Demo
Let us know how to reproduce the issue. Include a code sample, screen capture, video recording. The more inforation you provide, the better we can support you.
